data.description: The best value in Solera. Beautiful Community, so many amenities, low HOA’s! Located on an interior corner lot, this Mediterranean style, 2 bedroom, 2 bath home with an office is perfect for an easy, low maintenance lifestyle. In the kitchen features Corian countertops, cabinetry with convenient pull-out shelving, a lazy susan, a built-in microwave, dishwasher and tile flooring. The laundry room is located off the kitchen providing even more storage and direct access to the two car garage. The kitchen is open to the main entertaining area and that opens onto the private back patio and back yard. There are double pane windows and recessed lighting throughout. The spacious primary suite has windows to the enclosed back yard and the en-suite primary bath has double sinks and a walk-in shower. Down the main hall, to the right of the front entry is an office/den/hobby room. At the end of the hall, the secondary bedroom and guest full bath…A great layout.  Solera is a beautifully maintained and lovely  55+community with so many amenities! There’s a clubhouse with a large multi-purpose room, kitchen, billiard room, library and a full gym. A beautiful pool area with a salt water pool, just off the clubhouse, pickle ball and tennis courts, bocce ball courts. Beautiful greenbelts and lovely mountain views. Oak Valley Golf Course borders Solera and residents are offered special rates.
